This is an extremelly well done Puzzle game. It's challenging, while still being quite entertaining at the same time. 

PROS:
1.The musics are good;
2.Overall animations for enemies, and even the enviorements themselves, are extremelly well done;
3.The level and character designs (including bosses) are cool;
4.The gameplay itself feels fair and asks for you to think twice before doing something stupid;

CONS:
1.The gameplay CAN get a bit repetitive at times;

Overall, Fidel Dungeon Rescue is a great game for players/gamers who are searching for a challenge!
